# Committed demo — model service base URL.
#
# Point this at the deployed Space (running the base model for now) or your
# own backend. The demo calls POST {URL}/generate and GET {URL}/health.
#
# When this is left UNSET, the demo falls back to the bundled local mock at
# /api/committed-mock, which returns the same shape — so the page works with
# no backend configured.
#
# Must be prefixed NEXT_PUBLIC_ because the demo calls it from the browser.
NEXT_PUBLIC_COMMITTED_API_URL=
